-- Italy regulator bans short-selling of Finmeccanica shares
-- 
-- Tue Feb 12, 2013 6:57am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/02/12/us-finmeccanica-consob-idUSBRE91B0KM20130212

 

 MILAN  (Reuters) - Italy's market watchdog Consob said on Tuesday it had banned short selling on shares of defense group Finmeccanica ( SIFI.MI ) on Tuesday and Wednesday. 
 Earlier on Tuesday Italian police arrested the head of Finmeccanica in a corruption probe centered on the sale of helicopters to the Indian government. (Reporting By Stephen Jewkes)